# Python Flask Application

```python
from flask import Flask

app = Flask(__name__)

@app.route("/")
def home():
    return "DevOps Full Stack Project"

@app.route("/health")
def health():
    return "OK"

if __name__ == "__main__":
    app.run(
        host="0.0.0.0",
        port=5000
    )
```

